<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in West Springs</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Bordered by the estate homes and acreages of the Springbank community to the west, West Springs is a quiet and serene residential neighborhood in the South West quadrant of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">From the West Springs Co-Op to the West Springs Village and even the West Hills Towne Centre, there is a myriad of shopping destinations in and around the community in West springs. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Additionally, the residents can enjoy their leisure hours at the Westside Recreation Centre that houses exercise facilities, skating rinks, playgrounds, gymnasiums and a variety of both indoor and outdoor sports arenas.</p>
        </div>
